---
config:
theme: 'base'
themeVariables:
background: '#e0f7fa'
primaryColor: '#ffffff'
primaryTextColor: '#000000'
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant ALB as ALB
    participant API as API Service
    participant S3 as S3
    participant DDB as DynamoDB

    C->>ALB: POST /jobs (file + userId)
    ALB->>API: Forward request
    API->>API: Generate jobId (UUID)
    API->>S3: PutObject(uploads/jobId/fileName)
    S3-->>API: 200 OK
    API->>DDB: PutItem(jobId, status=HELD, userId, s3Key)
    DDB-->>API: 200 OK
    API-->>ALB: 201 Created
    ALB-->>C: {jobId, status: HELD}
